font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(27,40,57);
font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="微软雅黑" >一个用户只属于一个科学发现空间，登录后自动进入，不做多空间切换。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
