font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span style='font:7.0pt Times New Roman' >&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(27,40,57);
font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="微软雅黑" >一个空间对应一套自动化科学装置和一个主要学科领域。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.0000pt;margin-left:18.0000pt;
